{"id":39915,"date":"2023-04-23T18:58:58","date_gmt":"2023-04-23T14:58:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=39915"},"modified":"2023-04-23T18:58:58","modified_gmt":"2023-04-23T14:58:58","slug":"salawat-khams-jannah","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/23\/salawat-khams-jannah\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Salawat: Paradise for performing the five daily prayers"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Anas reported: A man asked the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, saying, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, how many prayers does Allah Almighty impose upon His servants?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Allah has obligated five prayers upon His servants.<\/strong>\u201d The man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, is there anything before or after them?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Allah has obligated five prayers upon His servants.<\/strong>\u201d The man swore an oath that he would not add or lessen anything of them. The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>If he is truthful, he will surely enter Paradise.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304&#8217;i\u0304 459<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Al-Albani<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0633\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064c \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0643\u064e\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0641\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0636\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639